wer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "童年创伤真的有那么大影响吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有时候会刷到一些视频说啊你现在的情况是什么什么的童年创伤造成的，什么性缘脑，能够体察人心啊，咋一看哇全中，然后就焦虑啊流泪啊崩溃啊觉得自己好惨好难哇。没有帮助，感觉这种视频简直是毫无正面意义的。我想的是我只能在哪一天看完一本有价值的心理书来完成自我的「进化」，又或者在经历哪一个事突然被「治愈」。 突然又觉得好可悲，面对身边同样经历的孩子，我又什么都做不到。我在被伤害想过一定不要让身边人重蹈覆辙，可是我做不到。我深刻的意识到我连自救都无法完成，更无法帮助他人了。我甚至不一定完成的了自救。只会有片刻的清醒。或许我会带着缺憾活一辈子，变成最讨厌的样子。谁能掌握未来呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/666034309"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ik43Ojr/4tedSEAMaCTExMDI4NTQ1NSCw5Ne2BjAAOBtAGnIJNjY2MDM0MzA5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1780949827.60882", "card_id": "Q_1955584635741382538", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "剩米饭除了炒着吃，还能怎样吃?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-565a75c9f691c9c5ea18984fd6700ab8_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1955584635741382538"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIk43Ojr/4tedSEAMaCTExNjc1NzcxMSD+w+LGBjAAOCdAG3ITMTk1NTU4NDYzNTc0MTM4MjUzOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1780949827.61109", "card_id": "Q_1970866161697690581", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 128}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高层住宅未来是不是垃圾资产？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e965f0499961b6f778df72c944c03998.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https